is the exact opposite.

00:07:43.800 --> 00:07:46.700 align:middle line:84%
It's all about
duality, separation,

00:07:46.700 --> 00:07:48.620 align:middle line:84%
so that the physical
plane becomes

00:07:48.620 --> 00:07:52.730 align:middle line:84%
our sealed alchemical
chamber in space and time

00:07:52.730 --> 00:07:56.000 align:middle line:84%
for us to go through
an alchemical change,

00:07:56.000 --> 00:08:00.080 align:middle line:84%
a spiritual development
process in our earthly life.

00:08:00.080 --> 00:08:03.590 align:middle line:84%
The split of unity into
duality is the foundation

00:08:03.590 --> 00:08:07.280 align:middle line:84%
