subconscious energy attractions

00:08:27.230 --> 00:08:30.440 align:middle line:84%
to unite and bring
forth children to bring

00:08:30.440 --> 00:08:33.270 align:middle line:90%
new life into the world.

00:08:33.270 --> 00:08:35.480 align:middle line:84%
