the same gender,

00:08:35.480 --> 00:08:40.730 align:middle line:84%
powerful complementary polarity
dynamics are still in play.

00:08:40.730 --> 00:08:43.669 align:middle line:84%
Ancient traditions knew
that this polarity split

00:08:43.669 --> 00:08:46.700 align:middle line:84%
and the resulting
attraction between opposites

00:08:46.700 --> 00:08:49.670 align:middle line:84%
