ultimate consciousness,

00:09:10.610 --> 00:09:14.930 align:middle line:84%
united with Shakti,
ultimate energy.

00:09:14.930 --> 00:09:17.720 align:middle line:84%
The cosmic yin and
yang energies which

00:09:17.720 --> 00:09:20.120 align:middle line:84%
