spirit core to manifest

00:09:20.120 --> 00:09:23.870 align:middle line:84%
as a child on the physical
plane manifest micro cosmically

00:09:23.870 --> 00:09:26.650 align:middle line:90%
through our mother and father.

00:09:26.650 --> 00:09:30.580 align:middle line:84%
