00:10:43.430 --> 00:10:46.220 align:middle line:84%
Once we have given someone
that role, of course

00:10:46.220 --> 00:10:48.260 align:middle line:84%
without informing
them of this, we

00:10:48.260 --> 00:10:50.730 align:middle line:84%
can then form a
relationship with them

00:10:50.730 --> 00:10:53.840 align:middle line:84%
and then fight with them
to endlessly recreate

00:10:53.840 --> 00:10:56.990 align:middle line:84%
