why we're behaving this way,

00:11:21.620 --> 00:11:23.990 align:middle line:84%
we end up in a power
struggle for who

00:11:23.990 --> 00:11:26.380 align:middle line:90%
will dominate the other.

00:11:26.380 --> 00:11:30.510 align:middle line:84%
We seek to punish our stand-in
for bad mommy or bad daddy

00:11:30.510 --> 00:11:32.850 align:middle line:84%
whenever they do not play
the role which we have

00:11:32.850 --> 00:11:35.040 align:middle line:90%
subconsciously assigned them.

00:11:35.040 --> 00:11:38.820 align:middle line:84%
This punishment can range from
our being passive aggressive,

00:11:38.820 --> 00:11:41.640 align:middle line:84%
meaning that we
are energetically

00:11:41.640 --> 00:11:45.330 align:middle line:84%
