the surface to be reasonable,

00:11:45.330 --> 00:11:47.760 align:middle line:84%
to escalating with
aggressive insults

00:11:47.760 --> 00:11:52.240 align:middle line:84%
and humiliation to outright
physical brutality.

00:11:52.240 --> 00:11:55.340 align:middle line:84%
Of course, this can never result
in the love which we really

00:11:55.340 --> 00:11:56.140 align:middle line:90%
seek.

00:11:56.140 --> 00:11:58.330 align:middle line:84%
It only destroys
whatever love was

00:11:58.330 --> 00:12:02.040 align:middle line:84%
present at the beginning
of the relationship.

00:12:02.040 --> 00:12:05.710 align:middle line:84%
When we survey so many
relationships between people,

00:12:05.710 --> 00:12:09.540 align:middle line:84%
we see again and again how
many people drawn together

00:12:09.540 --> 00:12:13.590 align:middle line:84%
in the hope of love actually
end up hurting and, in the end,

00:12:13.590 --> 00:12:16.030 align:middle line:90%
even hating each other.

00:12:16.030 --> 00:12:19.020 align:middle line:84%
So illuminating our
mommy daddy issues

