00:24:27.010 --> 00:24:31.000 align:middle line:84%
to free up our life energy and
neurolinguistic programming

00:24:31.000 --> 00:24:34.270 align:middle line:84%
to identify our
pain/pleasure associations

00:24:34.270 --> 00:24:38.700 align:middle line:84%
and to transform them, another
important modern development

00:24:38.700 --> 00:24:43.440 align:middle line:84%
was what became known as
transactional analysis.

00:24:43.440 --> 00:24:47.010 align:middle line:84%
Transactional analysis
means examining interactions

00:24:47.010 --> 00:24:51.490 align:middle line:84%
between people, the patterns
we create in our relationships.

00:24:51.490 --> 00:24:53.100 align:middle line:10%
It looks at how
our sense of self

00:24:53.100 --> 00:24:56.100 align:middle line:10%
is operating, whether
we are held back

00:24:56.100 --> 00:24:58.440 align:middle line:10%
at the stage of
acting like a child,

00:24:58.440 --> 00:25:00.390 align:middle line:10%
or do we act like a parent?

00:25:00.390 --> 00:25:05.530 align:middle line:10%
Or optimally, do we finally
learn how to become an adult?

00:25:05.530 --> 00:25:07.750 align:middle line:10%
Transactional analysis
also developed

00:25:07.750 --> 00:25:12.070 align:middle line:10%
the idea of life scripts,
how we internalize rules

00:25:12.070 --> 00:25:15.520 align:middle line:10%
from our environment to create
our own narrative about what

00:25:15.520 --> 00:25:19.150 align:middle line:10%
our life is about, who
we are, and all the rules

00:25:19.150 --> 00:25:21.980 align:middle line:10%
we have made for our lives.

00:25:21.980 --> 00:25:24.040 align:middle line:84%
What are your subconscious
rules about what

00:25:24.040 --> 00:25:26.200 align:middle line:90%
you need to be happy?

00:25:26.200 --> 00:25:29.830 align:middle line:84%
Is it large amounts of
money, material possessions,

00:25:29.830 --> 00:25:35.620 align:middle line:84%
social status, the love of a
particular specific individual?

00:25:35.620 --> 00:25:37.540 align:middle line:84%
Did you make a rule
that your happiness

00:25:37.540 --> 00:25:42.130 align:middle line:84%
depends on particular actions
by other people, people

00:25:42.130 --> 00:25:45.880 align:middle line:84%
who you will never be able to
control, people who are flawed

00:25:45.880 --> 00:25:48.820 align:middle line:84%
and struggling in their
own lives, who are highly

00:25:48.820 --> 00:25:52.420 align:middle line:84%
unlikely to be dependable in the
actions which you require them

00:25:52.420 --> 00:25:54.715 align:middle line:84%
to take in order
for you to be happy?

00:25:54.715 --> 00:25:57.193 align:middle line:90%


00:25:57.193 --> 00:25:58.610 align:middle line:84%
What are your rules
for what makes

00:25:58.610 --> 00:26:01.010 align:middle line:90%
a relationship successful?

00:26:01.010 --> 00:26:04.850 align:middle line:84%
Is it that it lasts forever
and is never changing?

00:26:04.850 --> 00:26:06.980 align:middle line:84%
If so, you're setting
yourself up for failure

00:26:06.980 --> 00:26:11.490 align:middle line:84%
and suffering because
people evolve and change.

00:26:11.490 --> 00:26:14.500 align:middle line:84%
Or did you make a rule that
a relationship was successful

00:26:14.500 --> 00:26:18.090 align:middle line:84%
if it created beautiful
moments, if it woke something up

00:26:18.090 --> 00:26:20.820 align:middle line:84%
in you and the other
person, if it helped you

00:26:20.820 --> 00:26:23.580 align:middle line:84%
both on your path
when it was right

00:26:23.580 --> 00:26:27.510 align:middle line:84%
and you separated lovingly
and without anger or hurt

00:26:27.510 --> 00:26:30.140 align:middle line:90%
when it had run its course?

00:26:30.140 --> 00:26:32.620 align:middle line:84%
Which set of rules do you think
is more likely to bring you

00:26:32.620 --> 00:26:35.620 align:middle line:90%
peace and happiness?

00:26:35.620 --> 00:26:37.480 align:middle line:90%
Relationships are not static.

00:26:37.480 --> 00:26:40.150 align:middle line:84%
Like everything alive,
they are dynamic.

00:26:40.150 --> 00:26:43.630 align:middle line:84%
And they must change and
evolve just as the people

00:26:43.630 --> 00:26:45.620 align:middle line:90%
in the relationship do.

00:26:45.620 --> 00:26:47.210 align:middle line:84%
Today, it is common
to see people

00:26:47.210 --> 00:26:51.200 align:middle line:84%
in intimate relationships
argue and blame their partner

00:26:51.200 --> 00:26:53.870 align:middle line:84%
for their own
unhappiness, saying things

00:26:53.870 --> 00:26:58.820 align:middle line:84%
like, you changed, as if change
is not permitted or healthy,

00:26:58.820 --> 00:27:02.960 align:middle line:84%
or saying, you promised me you
would do a particular thing

00:27:02.960 --> 00:27:05.180 align:middle line:84%
forever when the
other person is now

00:27:05.180 --> 00:27:07.520 align:middle line:84%
a very different person than
they were when they made

00:27:07.520 --> 00:27:11.030 align:middle line:90%
that promise years previously.

00:27:11.030 --> 00:27:13.460 align:middle line:84%
We have to understand
that no one can honestly

00:27:13.460 --> 00:27:17.600 align:middle line:84%
promise how they will feel
in any future situation.

00:27:17.600 --> 00:27:20.150 align:middle line:10%
We can be honest about
how we feel right now,

00:27:20.150 --> 00:27:22.520 align:middle line:10%
but we're lying
to ourselves if we

00:27:22.520 --> 00:27:26.930 align:middle line:10%
think we can commit to a feeling
that our future self will have

00:27:26.930 --> 00:27:29.420 align:middle line:10%
or even a perspective
on our relationship

00:27:29.420 --> 00:27:32.010 align:middle line:10%
that our future self will have.

00:27:32.010 --> 00:27:34.770 align:middle line:84%
Most of us can think back
to a time in our adolescence

00:27:34.770 --> 00:27:38.610 align:middle line:84%
when we were desperately madly
in love with another person.

00:27:38.610 --> 00:27:40.770 align:middle line:84%
We wanted a love
relationship with them

00:27:40.770 --> 00:27:42.990 align:middle line:90%
that would last forever.

00:27:42.990 --> 00:27:47.040 align:middle line:84%
When that relationship ended
or never came to fruition,

00:27:47.040 --> 00:27:48.810 align:middle line:84%
we felt like this was
the worst thing that

00:27:48.810 --> 00:27:51.390 align:middle line:84%
has ever happened
to any being ever

00:27:51.390 --> 00:27:53.070 align:middle line:90%
in the history of the world.

00:27:53.070 --> 00:27:54.840 align:middle line:84%
We felt like all of
our hopes and dreams

00:27:54.840 --> 00:27:59.370 align:middle line:84%
were crushed, that our suffering
was beyond measure, perhaps

00:27:59.370 --> 00:28:01.230 align:middle line:84%
leading to days,
months, sometimes

00:28:01.230 --> 00:28:05.110 align:middle line:84%
even years of depression
and inner collapse.

00:28:05.110 --> 00:28:07.380 align:middle line:84%
However, looking back
on it years later,

00:28:07.380 --> 00:28:11.130 align:middle line:84%
we often think, thank god I
didn't end up with that person.

00:28:11.130 --> 00:28:13.290 align:middle line:84%
What a catastrophe
that would have been.

00:28:13.290 --> 00:28:16.360 align:middle line:90%
I dodged a bullet.

00:28:16.360 --> 00:28:18.880 align:middle line:84%
To really understand the
range of relationships

00:28:18.880 --> 00:28:20.860 align:middle line:84%
we can create in
our lives, we have

00:28:20.860 --> 00:28:22.570 align:middle line:84%
to understand that
we are dynamically

00:28:22.570 --> 00:28:26.860 align:middle line:84%
evolving multidimensional
beings living on multiple planes

00:28:26.860 --> 00:28:29.170 align:middle line:90%
simultaneously.

00:28:29.170 --> 00:28:32.540 align:middle line:10%
We carry a portion of each of
the seven planes inside of us.

00:28:32.540 --> 00:28:35.020 align:middle line:84%
They are the literal
source of our subtle bodies

00:28:35.020 --> 00:28:36.430 align:middle line:90%
and our physical body.

00:28:36.430 --> 00:28:40.300 align:middle line:84%
We can create relationships
based on any of these planes,

00:28:40.300 --> 00:28:44.980 align:middle line:84%
or a particular relationship
can encompass multiple planes.

00:28:44.980 --> 00:28:47.020 align:middle line:10%
Real spiritual
development requires

00:28:47.020 --> 00:28:50.620 align:middle line:10%
that we become fully
conscious on each plane

00:28:50.620 --> 00:28:52.690 align:middle line:10%
through activating
and illuminating

00:28:52.690 --> 00:28:57.700 align:middle line:10%
our corresponding subtle
body level inside ourselves.

00:28:57.700 --> 00:28:59.740 align:middle line:84%
Forming relationships
with other people

00:28:59.740 --> 00:29:03.890 align:middle line:84%
on each level, the physical
level, the vitality level,

00:29:03.890 --> 00:29:06.610 align:middle line:84%
which is also the
source of our sexuality,

00:29:06.610 --> 00:29:09.850 align:middle line:84%
the emotional, mental,
spiritual, et cetera,

00:29:09.850 --> 00:29:13.630 align:middle line:84%
this is what helps us become
conscious of and to activate

00:29:13.630 --> 00:29:16.540 align:middle line:90%
each level within ourselves.

00:29:16.540 --> 00:29:20.650 align:middle line:84%
Relationships on all of these
levels are essential in order

00:29:20.650 --> 00:29:25.790 align:middle line:84%
for us to feel connected and
not have a lonely isolated life.

00:29:25.790 --> 00:29:29.060 align:middle line:84%
We need contact on the
physical and energy levels

00:29:29.060 --> 00:29:33.560 align:middle line:84%
through in-souled, loving
touch, which in our adult lives

00:29:33.560 --> 00:29:36.830 align:middle line:84%
can also become deep
sexual intimacy where

00:29:36.830 --> 00:29:41.330 align:middle line:84%
we exchange life energy
through our physical bodies.

00:29:41.330 --> 00:29:44.390 align:middle line:84%
We need contact on the
emotional and mental levels

00:29:44.390 --> 00:29:46.430 align:middle line:84%
so that we feel we have
people in our lives

00:29:46.430 --> 00:29:49.400 align:middle line:84%
who really know us,
who really see us,

00:29:49.400 --> 00:29:52.160 align:middle line:90%
who really understand us.

00:29:52.160 --> 00:29:54.710 align:middle line:84%
As we develop further,
our relationships

00:29:54.710 --> 00:29:57.770 align:middle line:84%
can extend into the causal
realm with an awareness

00:29:57.770 --> 00:30:00.290 align:middle line:84%
of the karmic connections
we develop with people

00:30:00.290 --> 00:30:04.670 align:middle line:84%
over multiple lifetimes
and then go even further

00:30:04.670 --> 00:30:08.360 align:middle line:84%
into spiritual
and divine levels.

00:30:08.360 --> 00:30:12.470 align:middle line:84%
It's deeply unrealistic to
think that one other person can

00:30:12.470 --> 00:30:18.020 align:middle line:84%
be our perfect optimal match
on all seven levels unchanging

00:30:18.020 --> 00:30:19.250 align:middle line:90%
forever.

00:30:19.250 --> 00:30:21.890 align:middle line:84%
The Earth is a
magical world where

00:30:21.890 --> 00:30:23.660 align:middle line:84%
we can encounter
and explore life

00:30:23.660 --> 00:30:26.870 align:middle line:84%
with a vast range of
other human beings.

00:30:26.870 --> 00:30:30.440 align:middle line:84%
We also have to understand
that we are being deeply unfair

00:30:30.440 --> 00:30:33.830 align:middle line:84%
to any person we get into a
relationship with who we then

00:30:33.830 --> 00:30:37.610 align:middle line:84%
saddle with the burden of
requiring them to provide all

00:30:37.610 --> 00:30:40.670 align:middle line:84%
of our connection
needs on all levels.

00:30:40.670 --> 00:30:42.680 align:middle line:84%
This just sets them
up for failure,

00:30:42.680 --> 00:30:45.860 align:middle line:84%
for disappointing us because
they're living their own life,

00:30:45.860 --> 00:30:46.760 align:middle line:90%
too.

00:30:46.760 --> 00:30:50.790 align:middle line:84%
They're not here just to play
an assigned role in our script.

00:30:50.790 --> 00:30:54.230 align:middle line:84%
We simply have to ask
ourselves, are we a match

00:30:54.230 --> 00:30:56.180 align:middle line:90%
with the other person?

00:30:56.180 --> 00:30:59.270 align:middle line:90%
If so, on what levels?

00:30:59.270 --> 00:31:03.620 align:middle line:84%
Is what I need and have
to offer a match for what

00:31:03.620 --> 00:31:06.110 align:middle line:84%
this person needs
and has to offer

00:31:06.110 --> 00:31:10.980 align:middle line:84%
on a particular level, whether
it be sexual, emotional,

00:31:10.980 --> 00:31:13.850 align:middle line:90%
mental, spiritual?

00:31:13.850 --> 00:31:16.730 align:middle line:84%
That one change in our
thoughts about relationships,

00:31:16.730 --> 00:31:20.720 align:middle line:84%
to see clearly whether or
not we are simply a match,

00:31:20.720 --> 00:31:24.380 align:middle line:84%
can make a huge contribution
to our replacing suffering

00:31:24.380 --> 00:31:27.030 align:middle line:90%
in our life with happiness.

00:31:27.030 --> 00:31:29.750 align:middle line:84%
All the anger and
resentment and blaming

00:31:29.750 --> 00:31:31.940 align:middle line:84%
we carry from
intimate relationships

00:31:31.940 --> 00:31:34.610 align:middle line:84%
can be released and
replaced with simply seeing

00:31:34.610 --> 00:31:37.640 align:middle line:84%
if it's a match or
not with no need

00:31:37.640 --> 00:31:40.850 align:middle line:84%
to assign blame or make
one person the villain

00:31:40.850 --> 00:31:43.800 align:middle line:90%
and the other person a victim.

00:31:43.800 --> 00:31:48.700 align:middle line:84%
As the old saying goes, the
only constant in life is change.

00:31:48.700 --> 00:31:51.480 align:middle line:84%
So what was once a match
with another person

00:31:51.480 --> 00:31:54.390 align:middle line:90%
at a particular level may end.

00:31:54.390 --> 00:31:56.220 align:middle line:84%
It's also possible
the relationship can

00:31:56.220 --> 00:32:01.800 align:middle line:84%
transform so that the two people
now match on a different level.

00:32:01.800 --> 00:32:04.170 align:middle line:84%
Many of our monogamous
relationships

00:32:04.170 --> 00:32:08.490 align:middle line:84%
are initially based on sexual
attraction and connection.

00:32:08.490 --> 00:32:11.160 align:middle line:84%
But in reality, for
most people, this

00:32:11.160 --> 00:32:15.580 align:middle line:84%
is the level that falls
away the most quickly.

00:32:15.580 --> 00:32:17.830 align:middle line:84%
When we connect at
the divine level,

00:32:17.830 --> 00:32:21.970 align:middle line:84%
we experience the true
nature of the term namaste,

00:32:21.970 --> 00:32:27.540 align:middle line:84%
the divine in me sees and
recognizes the divine in you.

00:32:27.540 --> 00:32:30.690 align:middle line:84%
At that stage, we can
truly merge into one.

00:32:30.690 --> 00:32:34.350 align:middle line:84%
A healthy relationship is based
on truly seeing and loving

00:32:34.350 --> 00:32:37.830 align:middle line:84%
the spiritual individuality
of our partner,

00:32:37.830 --> 00:32:41.190 align:middle line:84%
supporting them in their
dynamic evolution and growth

00:32:41.190 --> 00:32:44.730 align:middle line:84%
even if that path takes
them away from us.

00:32:44.730 --> 00:32:46.980 align:middle line:84%
The sacred geometry
of relationships

00:32:46.980 --> 00:32:50.100 align:middle line:84%
is one of the most profound
topics for our personal growth

00:32:50.100 --> 00:32:51.930 align:middle line:84%
and happiness,
which we've barely

00:32:51.930 --> 00:32:54.090 align:middle line:90%
scraped the surface of here.

00:32:54.090 --> 00:32:56.520 align:middle line:10%
For deeper applications
of the sacred geometry

00:32:56.520 --> 00:32:59.040 align:middle line:10%
of relationships
in our own lives,

00:32:59.040 --> 00:33:05.770 align:middle line:10%
please see my online
resources at www.vesica.org.

00:33:05.770 --> 00:33:08.440 align:middle line:84%
I'd like to leave you
with one final note.

00:33:08.440 --> 00:33:10.780 align:middle line:84%
Rather than the gloom
and doom we're constantly

00:33:10.780 --> 00:33:12.850 align:middle line:84%
faced with in our
world today, we

00:33:12.850 --> 00:33:16.270 align:middle line:84%
can instead choose to create a
bright future with new energy

00:33:16.270 --> 00:33:20.170 align:middle line:84%
sciences like cymatics,
vibrational radiesthesia,

00:33:20.170 --> 00:33:22.510 align:middle line:90%
and biogeometry.

00:33:22.510 --> 00:33:24.920 align:middle line:84%
I'm your host, Dr.
Robert J. Gilbert.

00:33:24.920 --> 00:33:27.880 align:middle line:84%
Thank you so much for
joining me for this series.

00:33:27.880 --> 00:33:30.460 align:middle line:10%
It's been my great privilege
to explore with you

00:33:30.460 --> 00:33:33.150 align:middle line:10%
the secrets of Sacred Geometry.

